Summary: I went outside and saw and upside-down shaped object from my backyard.
divs: Sighting DetailsI went outside around 9:15 and saw an upside down triangle shaped object in the western sky. It changed from blue to gold to silver, and then faded to no color, but you could still see light reflecting off of it like glass. I preceding to get my cell phone and took a series of pictures. I came in for a minute to see if my mother could come outside. She couldn't. When i came back outside it was glowing very brightly. I saw another object leave the main object at a slow rate of speed. It had a diamond shape and had A bright light on top(you can see it in one of the pictures) (The bright gold in one of the pictures is a streetlight).
